ABOUT US
The dynamic social life of GlenLakes revolves around the 35,000 square-foot clubhouse. Here you can choose from a variety of dining options, take a computer or ceramics class, attend a lecture and stay in shape with a fitness class or personalized workout. Or, just gather a few friends for a friendly game of billiards or a cocktail at the clubhouse bar and lounge. And with so much multipurpose space, the clubhouse is perfect for private functions, meetings and lavish special events.
VISIT THE CLUB
Florida Living that Borders on the Wild
Nature lovers, fitness aficionados, golfers and those who love an action-packed social life—
GlenLakes is it!
Adjoining the 85,000-acre Chassahowitzka National Wildlife Refuge, which borders the Gulf of Mexico, GlenLakes captures everything you love about the Florida lifestyle: stunning views, championship golf, country club amenities, a gated, 24-hour manned entrance, immaculately maintained community and captivating home designs, perfect for entertaining and relaxation.
In the Action, Yet Surrounded by Tranquility
GlenLakes is located in Weeki Wachee, Florida, part of Florida’s Nature Coast. Natural springs, lakes, the Weeki Wachee River, the Gulf of Mexico and thousands of acres of nature preserve provide a pristine habitat for wildlife, flora and fauna—and year-round opportunities for outdoor enthusiasts.
In a word, the location is perfect.

MEMBERSHIPS
Unprecedented Golf Value. Priceless Benefits.
GlenLakes Golf Membership offers the privileges of a private club—without the typical private club price tag. Members enjoy unlimited tee times as well as the opportunity to play in tournaments and enjoy special events. All golf members are invited to join one of the club associations, The GlenLakes Men’s Golf Association or The GlenLakes Ladies’ Golf Association. It’s a great way to share your love of the game with fellow enthusiasts.
For those that aren’t golfers but want to live a full social life, there is a membership for you as well! Social Membership allows use of all of the Clubhouse amenities such as pool, pickleball, restaurants, fitness center and more.
Ask your sales specialist about more details on either membership and incentives.
Membership initiation fees are waived when you purchase a home through the GlenLakes realty office.
